headline: Strength Seen in International Flavors (IFF): Can Its 9.2% Jump Turn into More Strength?
summary: International Flavors (IFF) saw its shares surge in the last session with trading volume being higher than average. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions may not translate into further price increase in the near term.

headline: IFF Opens Mexico Business Hub at Tecnoparque
summary: NEW YORK, April 10, 2025--To further strengthen its ability to serve customers with leading innovations, IFF (NYSE: IFF) announced it will combine the majority of its business operations in Mexico at a new site in Mexico City within the Tecnoparque business complex. The move will begin immediately with its Global Business Services Center—which supports the company’s full business capabilities serving Mexican and Latin American markets—and is expected to finalize by 2026.
